## Usage
Run in a terminal inside the *"inventorymanag"* project folder.

Remember that it is necessary to have [Docker](https://www.docker.com/products/docker-desktop/) installed on the PC and to have solved WSL problems.

```bash
docker compose build --no-cache
```
After the necessary dependencies are installed (automatic), run the following command within the same terminal:
```bash
docker compose up -d
```

#### Done pana rabbit, now you can check that everything is ok through the following URLs:

```bash
Frontend | App React                   -> http://127.0.0.1:3000/
Backend  | API Rest - Python           -> http://127.0.0.1:8008/
Backend  | CRUD request guide && URLs  -> http://127.0.0.1:8008/docs

```
